snippet.title: Far Cry 2's weird Java phone port (FC2 Spoilers) | minimme
snippet.description:
THIS VIDEO CONTAINS FAR CRY 2 SPOILERS

Far Cry 2 had a J2ME game for some reason and it's weird so I made a video on it!

Full let's play of this game: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wos_YhIbV88
